  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then later came the Americans up too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we were called-- when I say it, the Danish Brigade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we got an American name, because it was all under Eisenhower and Montgomery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were called Dan Force.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- our military unit was called.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we've got the border patrol together with the British, and that meant that we now were throwing out all the Germans from Denmark.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is of course 1945 now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from-- from the 5th of May to the end of July, when we were sent home, because in that span of time, the Danish military already were functioning that we had-- all our units had come in.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- what shall I say-- the directors of the units and all, with the former Danish military, was all called up again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so new Danish units were called back into service.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in July, they were all ready.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we relinquished all our weapons, and that was it at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
